  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    CarDiagnosticEvent
    A CarDiagnosticEvent object corresponds to a single diagnostic event frame coming from the car.
    CarDiagnosticEvent.Builder
    This class can be used to incrementally construct a CarDiagnosticEvent.

    Contains information about ignition monitors common to all vehicle types.
    CarDiagnosticEvent.CompressionIgnitionMonitors
    Contains information about ignition monitors specific to compression vehicles.
    CarDiagnosticEvent.FuelSystemStatus
    Represents possible states of the fuel system; see IntegerSensorIndex.FUEL_SYSTEM_STATUS
    CarDiagnosticEvent.FuelType
    Represents possible types of fuel; see IntegerSensorIndex.FUEL_TYPE
    CarDiagnosticEvent.IgnitionMonitor
    Represents the state of an ignition monitor on a vehicle.
    CarDiagnosticEvent.IgnitionMonitor.Decoder  
    CarDiagnosticEvent.SecondaryAirStatus
    Represents possible states of the secondary air system; see IntegerSensorIndex.COMMANDED_SECONDARY_AIR_STATUS
    CarDiagnosticEvent.SparkIgnitionMonitors
    Contains information about ignition monitors specific to spark vehicles.
    CarDiagnosticManager
    API for monitoring car diagnostic data.
    FloatSensorIndex
    This class is a container for the indices of diagnostic sensors.
    IntegerSensorIndex
    This class is a container for the indices of diagnostic sensors.
